# Default ignores baked into the Stoat binary and applied to every
# workspace's file finder. Users can extend per-repo with their own
# `.stoatignore`; entries here apply via the walker's `filter_entry`,
# which runs after the ignore stack, so per-repo negations do not
# override these defaults.
#
# Syntax: standard gitignore.

.git/
node_modules/
target/
